{
  "chapter": 16,
  "chapter_summary": "第十六回「虎穴娇娃」。八方镖局总镖头戴高岗以护送之名，将与吕迪交手后重伤的叶开扶上马车，喂以含料的参汤，意图将其交予金钱帮。叶开识破机关，借机将含参汤的口水吐在戴高岗独食的鸡腿上，反令其昏睡，自己悄然脱身。马车被金钱帮眼线赶入山中仿长安街道的鸿宾客栈，戴高岗惊醒发现叶开失踪，被上官小仙逼问。上官小仙微笑间以镶银象牙筷欲取戴高岗性命——所谓「先让他休息二十年」。千钧一发之际，叶开以飞刀断筷钉墙，救下戴高岗，称两人人情已结清。叶开明知是陷阱却坦然重返，面对上官小仙的言语试探，从容以口水计反讥，并坦言「已没有别的地方可去」，与上官小仙展开一场势均力敌的心理交锋。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "speaker_name": "戴高岗",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你的伤不轻，一定要赶快去找个好大夫。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "text": "你本不该这么样对我的，我对你的态度并不好。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "speaker_name": "戴高岗",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "无论谁在你当时那种心情下，态度都不会好的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "text": "看来我不但低估了吕迪，也看错了你。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "speaker_name": "戴高岗",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "他的确是我生平未见的高手，但却还是未必能比得上你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "text": "我已败了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "speaker_name": "戴高岗",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "可是他若真的要杀你，现在也已死在你手下。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "text": "你也相信这句话？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "text": "你知不知道在墙外说这句话的人是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "speaker_name": "戴高岗",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我正想问你，你一定知道他是谁的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "speaker_name": "戴高岗",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我想他一定是你的朋友。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "speaker_name": "戴高岗",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "因为他不但帮你说出了你不愿说的话，而且生怕吕迪再下毒手，所以故意将他引开。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "text": "你想得的确很周到，却想错了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "speaker_name": "戴高岗",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "这个人不是你的朋友？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "text": "我本来以为也是我的朋友。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "speaker_name": "戴高岗",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "现在呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "text": "现在我只希望以前永远没有见过他，以后也永远不要见到他。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "speaker_name": "戴高岗",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你知道他是什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "text": "你要带我去找的大夫是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "speaker_name": "戴高岗",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "那个大夫也是个很古怪的人，医道却很高。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "text": "我昨天也认得了一个人很古怪，医道很高明的郎中。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "speaker_name": "戴高岗",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "医道高明的大夫，脾气好像都有点古怪的，就正如真正的武林高手，脾气也都有点古怪一样。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "text": "你的脾气并不古怪。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "speaker_name": "戴高岗",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我怎么能算武功高手？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "text": "但我却知道，近年来八方镖局保的镖，从来也没有出过一次岔子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "speaker_name": "戴高岗",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "那只不过因为我这两年来的运气不错，而且有很多好朋友照顾。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "text": "我相信你一定有很多好朋友。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "speaker_name": "戴高岗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "停车！",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "speaker_name": "戴高岗",
      "listener": "char_gan_che_de",
      "text": "你有没有看见那姓叶的下车？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_che_de",
      "speaker_name": "赶车的",
      "listener": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "speaker_name": "戴高岗",
      "listener": "char_gan_che_de",
      "text": "他的人呢？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_che_de",
      "speaker_name": "赶车的",
      "listener": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "text": "你跟他一起在车里，你不知道，我怎么知道？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_che_de",
      "speaker_name": "赶车的",
      "listener": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "text": "你最好还是赶快上车，跟我一齐去交差。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_ji",
      "speaker_name": "伙计",
      "listener": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "text": "戴总镖头是一人来的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "speaker_name": "戴高岗",
      "listener": "char_huo_ji",
      "text": "只有一个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_ji",
      "speaker_name": "伙计",
      "listener": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "text": "房间早已替总镖头准备好了，请随我来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "text": "你一个人来的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "speaker_name": "戴高岗",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "text": "还有个人呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "speaker_name": "戴高岗",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "走了。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "text": "你难道是在说，叶开已走了？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "text": "我要你替他准备的那碗参汤，他没有喝？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "speaker_name": "戴高岗",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "他……他喝了。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "text": "然后呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "speaker_name": "戴高岗",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "然后我就扶他上了车。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "text": "在车上他睡着了没有？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "speaker_name": "戴高岗",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "睡着了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "text": "他的伤势怎么样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "speaker_name": "戴高岗",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "伤得不轻。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "text": "这我就不懂了，一个受了重伤，又睡着了的人，你怎么会放他走的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "speaker_name": "戴高岗",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "我……我没有放他走。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "text": "我也知道是他自己要走的，可是你难道就不能留住他。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "speaker_name": "戴高岗",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "他走的时候，我根本不知道。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "text": "你跟他不是坐一辆车来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "speaker_name": "戴高岗",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "text": "这又奇怪了，你跟他坐在一辆车上，他走的时候，你怎么会不知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "speaker_name": "戴高岗",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "因为……因为……因为我也睡着了。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "text": "我知道你一定也很累，最近你一直都忙得很。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "speaker_name": "戴高岗",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "我……我不累，一点也不累。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "text": "你的应酬那么多，不但要应酬客人，还得要应酬那些大大小小的妖精，怎么会不累呢？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "text": "我想你已经应该好好的休息一阵子了，我就先让你休息二十年吧。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "speaker_name": "戴高岗",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "二……二十年？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "text": "二十年后，你一定又是条生龙活虎般的好汉了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_dai_gao_gang",
      "text": "你救我一次，我也救你一次，现在我们的人情已结清。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我说的果然不错，你身上果然不止带着一把刀的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "吕迪呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "他怎么会追得上我？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "除了你之外，世上还有什么男人能追得上我。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "这真是个好地方。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你喜欢这地方？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "我若一直睡着，到现在才醒，一定以为还在城里，一定想不到金钱帮的总舵会在这么样一个地方。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "只可惜你好像是不肯好好睡一下的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "我的应酬并不多，认得的妖精也只有一个，所以我总是不太累。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我本来以为你会很累的，最近我看到你的时候，你总是在床上，床上的妖精，却不止一个，所以特地叫人替你准备了碗参汤，养养你的元气，谁知你居然不领情。",
      "tone": "吃吃",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "我已领过了情。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "那碗参汤你真的喝了下去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "只可惜那碗参汤下的补药还不够，若要叫我真的睡一觉，最少也得用十来斤补药才行。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "这只怪我，竟忘了你是魔教中大公主的大少爷。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "所以你不能怪戴总镖头，我相信他自己也不知道自己是怎么会睡着的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "可是你知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "我一上车，就发现了他为他自己一个人准备的酒菜。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你身上难道也总是带着能令人睡着的补药？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "我只不过吐了点口水在他鸡腿上。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你的口水里还有参汤？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "所以那条鸡腿的滋味一定很不错。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你怎么知道这位戴总镖头是想带你来找我的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "口水里的一点参汤，就能让人睡着，那种参汤除了你之外，还有谁能做得出？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你既然已走了，为什么还要来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "因为我好像已没有别的地方可去。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    }
